25690152\"},{\"title\":\"2025 AI 编程新范式：IDE 负责“微观补全”，qoder-cli 负责“宏观 Agent”\",\"url\":\"https://juejin.cn/post/7587336857538674697\"},{\"title\":\"阿里Qoder深度评测：与TRAE SOLO、CodeBuddy IDE的横向对比分析\",\"url\":\"https://wk.baidu.com/view/27007a0e6885ec3a87c24028915f804d2b168764\"}]\n\nBased on my search results, I found information about several AI coding IDEs that were mentioned in the context of February 2025 or as alternatives to Cursor and Windsurf. Here's what I discovered:\n\n## AI Coding IDEs and Alternatives to Cursor/Windsurf\n\n### **No Specific IDE Launch in February 2025**\nI did not find any AI coding IDE that was specifically launched in February 2025. However, there are several notable alternatives to Cursor and Windsurf mentioned:\n\n---\n\n### **Major AI IDE Alternatives:**\n\n#### **1. Trae (ByteDance)**\n- **Launch context:** Introduced in 2025\n- **Developer:** ByteDance (字节跳动)\n- **Key features:**\n  - Free to use with GPT-4/Claude models\n  - Optimized for Chinese users\n  - Two versions: domestic (trae.cn) and international (trae.ai)\n  - AI-native IDE with adaptive capabilities\n  - SOLO mode for autonomous development\n- **Price:** Free tier available, Pro at ~$9.95/month\n\n#### **2. Qoder (Alibaba)**\n- **Launch:** August 22, 2025\n- **Developer:** Alibaba Cloud\n- **Key features:**\n  - Agentic Coding Platform\n  - Can index up to 100,000 code files\n  - Quest Mode for task delegation\n  - Repo Wiki (automatic project documentation)\n  - Multi-model intelligent routing\n  - Long and short-term memory system\n- **Price:** Free preview, Pro at $20/month (first month $2)\n\n#### **3. Zed**\n- **Language:** Built with Rust\n- **Features:** High performance, real-time collaboration, AI assistance\n- **Price:** Free + $20/month for premium\n\n#### **4. PearAI**\n- **Positioning:** Open-source alternative to Cursor\n- **Features:** Multi-model support\n- **Price:** Free + $15/month\n\n---\n\n### **Established AI IDEs:**\n\n| IDE | Developer | Key Features | Price |\n|-----|-----------|--------------|-------|\n| **Cursor** | Anysphere | Multi-file editing, Agent mode, YOLO mode | $20/month |\n| **Windsurf** | Codeium | Cascade agent mode, deep context understanding | $15/month |\n| **GitHub Copilot** | Microsoft | Deep GitHub ecosystem integration | $10/month |\n\n---\n\n**Note:** If you're looking for a specific AI IDE that was announced in February 2025, could you provide more details such as:\n- The company name\n- Specific features\n- Where you heard about it\n\nThis would help me search more precisely for the exact tool you're referring to.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
