term popularized by Andrej Karpathy in February 2025, describing a new approach to AI-assisted programming\n\n### Important Note About Search Limitations\n\nThe search results I found don't include specific \"Show HN\" posts with titles, URLs, or Hacker News discussion threads from February 2025. This could be because:\n- The site-specific searches didn't return Hacker News content properly\n- There may not have been notable \"Show HN\" posts for AI coding tools specifically in February 2025\n- The search tools had difficulty indexing Hacker News content from that specific timeframe\n\nWould you like me to try a different search approach or focus on specific aspects of AI coding agents from that time period?\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
